id: hac-em8a
title: Restore reproducible Dependabot CI and modernize actions
description: Fix the shared frozen-lockfile failure and update deprecated GitHub Actions majors.
type: Issue
status: in_progress
priority: 1
tags[4]: ci,dependabot,github-actions,reproducibility
created_at: "2026-07-16T16:54:19.097Z"
